{"tid":2257623,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2013年爭鋪路 冀47億照顧20人","createTime":"2020-10-25T10:29:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T10:29:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1e2d4f153a5bb3031a30bf165013f01848d48ea2","tid":2257623,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T10:29:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201025/YZWM73VLXZAX7BFZMRZMW7LWG4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201025%2FYZWM73VLXZAX7BFZMRZMW7LWG4%2F&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=967f3a51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201025%2FYZWM73VLXZAX7BFZMRZMW7LWG4%2F&h=4b28262d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201025/YZWM73VLXZAX7BFZMRZMW7LWG4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n2013年爭鋪路 冀47億照顧20人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IpoWZKZ6RIwPlHURWT-30-KLmNc=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V7ELIH3CO5CN5P3WEUIWWQY62A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIpoWZKZ6RIwPlHURWT-30-KLmNc%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV7ELIH3CO5CN5P3WEUIWWQY62A.jpg&h=440a8fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【2020年】■沙螺灣村本月初再封村，有村民坐在閘內看守。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】月初沙螺灣村突然封村，聲稱為阻止日漸增多的行山客滋擾居民。其實今次只是重施故技，村民早在2013年11月就曾「無限期封村」示威，要求政府「兌現承諾」興建車路連接東涌和大澳，村民擾攘至翌年初才肯解封。政府近年曾估算有關車路的建造費高達47億元，但村內的常住人口卻只剩20人。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：鐵閘拆一起三 狂砍樹霸地 「沙螺灣國」拓車路冇王管<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XtEDCxLweC73_LRM3s9azQBX7n0=/2096x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6EBPAUJ56RA43ICT33IYVUZ6PI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXtEDCxLweC73_LRM3s9azQBX7n0%3D%2F2096x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6EBPAUJ56RA43ICT33IYVUZ6PI.jpg&h=3a093d04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【2013年】■村民早年已在東澳古道上加設鐵閘阻擋遊人，爭取建路。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/p-2Iyhcf4JEf62xok9hhvS7wEuk=/2406x1604/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UYBM6HA7SRGHZK2G7AHYQTTBFM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fp-2Iyhcf4JEf62xok9hhvS7wEuk%3D%2F2406x1604%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUYBM6HA7SRGHZK2G7AHYQTTBFM.jpg&h=1b5fd312&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■前村長李志峯（左）多次透過傳媒要求政府興建車路；右為現任村長李秀梅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一日僅四班渡輪途經<br />\n<br />\n現時沙螺灣村的對外交通倚賴由屯門來往大澳的渡輪服務，平日每日有四班途經沙螺灣。村民以往亦可選擇中環來往大澳的渡輪，但該航線最終在1983年因虧損問題而結束。政府於是計劃由羌山道興建總長約4.6公里的支路，以連接深屈和沙螺灣等地。<br />\n<br />\n工程分兩期進行，第一期由大澳道通往深屈的道路早在1990年已經完成。第二期工程展開前，路政署委託政府統計處重新統計沿。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n自此，時任村長李志峯就不斷透過傳媒要求政府興建。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n2014年，由地產商把持的大嶼山發展諮詢委員會就曾討論由。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n土木工程拓展署及後在2017年展開《檢視大嶼山的交通運輸基建網絡及旅客接待能力的研究》，。。。。。。。"}]}